First she restricts him and ties him up into the pillory. Without any way to escape he has to endure the endless mind games of the Baroness. Mr. Chambers withstands the interrogation but the Baroness cannot hold her inner sadistic feelings any longer. She simply must abuse him with mummification, extreme bondage, and intensive nipple torment. But Mr. Chambers is still not ready to talk. More extensive measures need to be taken. It is time to brutally peg his unwilling hole to get him talking.
title: Ep 1 - Caught and Interrogated: In the Dungeon of The Baroness
